text:
When a receiving UM RLC entity receives UMD PDUs, it shall:
- detect the loss of RLC SDU segments at lower layers;
- reassemble RLC SDUs from the received UMD PDUs and deliver the RLC SDUs to upper layer as soon as they
are available;

- discard received UMD PDUs that cannot be re-assembled into an RLC SDU due to loss at lower layers of an
UMD PDU which belonged to the particular RLC SDU.

